name: Ina Narrative Fangame
description: Press SPACE bar to start the game. Then,  use WASD to jiggle around Ina's coral yard. You will encounter theGaurd Takodachi in your venture and once you do, press space to talk to them as well as Ina herself if you overcome the grueling trials, the twists and turns, the laboring endeavor to finally meet her. Don't forget to pay close attention to what instructions they're saying! Otherwise, you'll be stuck in this fishy fever dream forever.
